data.meta_description: New York: Tor, 1999 . Octavo, boards. First edition. Stand-alone prequel to A FIRE UPON THE DEEP 1992 . Winner of the 2000 Hugo award. Anatomy of Wonder 2004 II-1190. data.text:
Vinge, Vernor. A DEEPNESS IN THE SKY. New York: Tor, [1999]. Octavo, boards. First edition. Stand-alone prequel to A FIRE UPON THE DEEP (1992). Winner of the 2000 Hugo award. Anatomy of Wonder (2004) II-1190. Sargent, British and American Utopian Literature, 1986-2009. Small dent in lower edge of front board, else a fine copy in fine dust jacket with mild matching bruise. (#168073).

Price: $100.00
